episodes.title: Is Tulsi Gabbard in a CULT?
episodes.description:
Donald Trump has tapped Tulsi Gabbard to be his Director of National Intelligence. But her connections to the group Science of Identity Foundation (SIF) have people wondering if she is a cult member.
